name: ICE BABY ❄️
description: This piece is dedicated to one of greatest rappers of his time. Ice Cube, A king from famous rap group “N.W.A” but who’s from the roots Crenshaw in California. One of best to come out of Compton, with a flow that was and is still second to none till this day, ice cube was an iconic rapper, a fan favorite , ICEE was top 3 and trust me he wasn’t number 3. Hope you guys love this one. Most especially its a piece to celebrate my 19th birthday
